Hi
i have done alot to this map to make it as good as it could be...
i think i could have done more...
like fog
or somthing
but it has alot of things to it :)
it has lights that act like thunder...
a 3d skybox and hdr...
it has some things that break when you use the leaver / cross thing
lol
it also has bits that are like physics but is a brush... (a physbox)
so when the things that keep it up break it falls down into the water
the water hurts you if you go all fall in...
so dont walk in and think you are going to own all the other team...
lol
all this lags a small bit...
but not too much (as i have a bad pc)
i did not put a nav file in it as the bots did not work...
and just jumped of the hills into the water...
and died XP

if you post.... assess

thanks for looking at my map!
:)
